{"tid":2488494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[窮人生仔正仆街] 我為樓狂｜網傳兒子控訴 要求阿媽賣樓分300萬 疾呼「我要嘅係尊重」","createTime":"2021-04-14T09:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T09:49:13.000Z","uid":251732,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"64affa2f7325c41f1f5b3febd89c618e1dafe5bc","tid":2488494,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"...最近網上流傳一輯圖片，疑似有兒子要求阿媽賣樓分身家，更大咬要分300萬元，疑索價不果，將全屋家具推倒慘變成「廢墟」，並要報<del>警</del>狗求助。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TfhrzSE0K9ggH6Vzm2v2A3asebk=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R4GVYEVJL5FIXJ4ROKYOOHZ6XE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTfhrzSE0K9ggH6Vzm2v2A3asebk%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR4GVYEVJL5FIXJ4ROKYOOHZ6XE.jpg&h=21c311aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-sl76X5ou4lAnu1vqBusBRd_Ff4=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YPPFFCC5FRCPLOEIWLM24KK434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-sl76X5ou4lAnu1vqBusBRd_Ff4%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYPPFFCC5FRCPLOEIWLM24KK434.jpg&h=41055285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/K1jwIE2X9hHjwqitm-FrVl_LPm0=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O3YIXUURZ5DJDJISVIVH6IQUQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FK1jwIE2X9hHjwqitm-FrVl_LPm0%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO3YIXUURZ5DJDJISVIVH6IQUQE.jpg&h=3e3f3479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k74S0d3nPuxESr54X905J062bkQ=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VEOJDADOR5CV7J7TCTBZDTZ5LI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk74S0d3nPuxESr54X905J062bkQ%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVEOJDADOR5CV7J7TCTBZDTZ5LI.jpg&h=38ab751e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mG2K5l1PhQ__pAcMxJ6gqftQypc=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GX3G25T2KVESNI3ZI6EDF2XXVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmG2K5l1PhQ__pAcMxJ6gqftQypc%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGX3G25T2KVESNI3ZI6EDF2XXVE.jpg&h=4c7b7ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RH-Rz3iGOsXyw43a-zgEO3VthQ4=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GEHAVISRGZAWREPP3MLQQSJ45Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRH-Rz3iGOsXyw43a-zgEO3VthQ4%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGEHAVISRGZAWREPP3MLQQSJ45Y.jpg&h=ececf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/aQ1YNHZ0jYYPj3h2KBRxq7pJD6M=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A4RRR4I3PZBYTBK37JVRGOXTUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FaQ1YNHZ0jYYPj3h2KBRxq7pJD6M%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA4RRR4I3PZBYTBK37JVRGOXTUY.jpg&h=4697fa75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Qvx4yFNZrw67cKs3G2hWlegxztM=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F2LZDPDZDBEMVLXFRC3SBL6AHI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQvx4yFNZrw67cKs3G2hWlegxztM%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF2LZDPDZDBEMVLXFRC3SBL6AHI.jpg&h=63b757a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日網上流傳一輯照片，指有人「要阿媽賣樓分錢唔成拆屋泄憤」，照片可見，一個住宅單位客廳至睡房均被人搗亂，客廳雜物散落一地，十分凌亂，梳化、抽屜、地面均滿佈家中物品。電視機及枱燈被人推倒在地上。<br />\n<br />\n「To 老媽，我想你應該還不是很明白。我不是在外住到6月份。我係要分一半房屋的價錢，3百萬。之後過我自己的生活。我不會回來的了。」 <br />\n「我要嘅係尊重，對自由、尊嚴、平等嘅待遇。自己的私生活、工作都與你和任何人無關。」房門亦大大隻字寫上「賣樓」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210414/VNSFZYHRAZBWNKDOSOMVNEAVTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210414%2FVNSFZYHRAZBWNKDOSOMVNEAVTE%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzviK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=fe2dbfd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210414%2FVNSFZYHRAZBWNKDOSOMVNEAVTE%2F&h=f42e8a54\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210414/VNSFZYHRAZBWNKDOSOMVNEAVTE/</a>"},{"pid":"5744c447d824bb492c7a39e17be33234fec85df9","tid":2488494,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:26:19.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"c1b70a49774fcb1246c45897669a1548b25d805f","tid":2488494,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"dc537d62e2334017ca31c9ac62b14634fb7ab23